            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p>Welcome to Bookstore! Founded in 2020, we are a dedicated team of book enthusiasts committed to bringing you the best selection of books. Our store is more than just a place to buy books; it as a haven for book lovers and a community space where readers can connect.</p>
